Glencore International Plc Chief 
Executive Officer Ivan Glasenberg said the company’s 23 
billion pound ($36.3 billion) all-share offer for  Xstrata Plc (XTA)  
is a “fair price,” rebuffing calls from some investors to 
raise it. (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 02:10
 